          experimental weather software system written in Python. Weewx was designed to be simple,
          fast, and easy to understand by leveraging modern software concepts.
        </p>
      </div> <!-- End id "about" -->
      
      
    <div class="clr"></div>

    </div> <!-- End id "page" -->
        
